Pre-Game Insights: Mitchell Marsh will lead the Australian side, while Richie Berrington will captain Scotland.
The series is significant for both teams, with Australia looking to rebuild after the T20 World Cup and Scotland aiming for a historic series win.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The live streaming will be available on the FanCode app and website.
Australia and Scotland have played one T20I before, with Australia winning by five wickets.
